author: Oliver Smith
title: Can you name the islands from their outlines?
text: With thousands of Britons currently enjoying holidays on sun-soaked Mediterranean isles, we've been inspired to devise the following quiz. A few summer favourites will crop up, as will some lesser-known spots. And a word of caution: don't get all cocky if you answer the first few correctly, because each question is harder than the last. Once you're done, try our quizzes on British seaside resorts , weird driving laws , airport codes , world flags and obscure capital cities . Telegraphtravel Follow @telegraphtravel
